articles.title: Iran: US ‘can NOT renege’ on deal to transfer $6 billion through Qatar for hostages - The Times of Israel
articles.description: Tehran demands funds promised in exchange for 5 American prisoners released in August, after Washington halts process in wake of devastating Hamas assault on Israel
articles.content:
Iran said Friday the United States “can not renege” on an agreement to transfer $6 billion in frozen funds through mediator Qatar following Hamas’s catastrophic assault on Israeli communities.
